0.content: Hello! My name is Santeri, and I'm a 5th year IT student at Hervanta campus of Tampere University (previously known as Tampere University of Technology). I'm interested in projects that have a real effect on the world, no matter if it's only software or something not related to software at all. The best way to reach me is by telegram or email, you can begin by introducing yourself. This is the base Jekyll theme.
